title: Ep 49 - How You Do One Thing is How You do Everything
itunes:title: Ep 49 - How You Do One Thing is How You do Everything
description:
Most people feel it is okay to come up short on the little things in life as long as the finish the bigger things. In this episode we talk about the importance of giving a little bit extra and shooting for more than you planned, even on the little things in life. Because if you go over and above on the little things then you will execute your larger goals in life at a much higher level.
